1
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,030
[The Princess Royal]

2
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:27,890
[Adapted from Mo Shubai's novel,
The Princess Royal]

3
00:01:27,890 --> 00:01:28,950
[on Jinjiang Original Network]

4
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

5
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 6]

6
00:01:33,180 --> 00:01:33,940
Pei Wenxuan,

7
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:36,940
This is the imperial court.

8
00:01:37,220 --> 00:01:38,540
How could you use a folk song

9
00:01:38,540 --> 00:01:39,780
as court evidence?

10
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:41,100
If the rumors are indeed true,

11
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:43,980
would you let His Majesty be deceived?

12
00:01:43,980 --> 00:01:47,420
If we let tyrants fill the streets

13
00:01:47,660 --> 00:01:48,700
and be revered by the people,

14
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:51,540
we'd be a joke for millennia to come.

15
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:53,900
Blasphemy! This is nonsense!

16
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:55,300
You're just trying to bring chaos!

17
00:01:55,580 --> 00:01:57,860
Mr. Wang, if you think I'm lying,

18
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,460
why do you appear so angry?

19
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,100
Perhaps...

20
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:04,900
you are related to this matter?

21
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,220
H-How am I involved?

22
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,060
Pei Wenxuan,

23
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:11,700
if your words were to obstruct the truth

24
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:14,020
and cause instability of the borders,

25
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,460
how shall you be punished?

26
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:17,780
Mr. Xie,

27
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:21,300
I am merely giving suggestions,

28
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:23,700
yet you accuse me
of obstructing the truth.

29
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:25,540
If we do not get to the bottom of this,

30
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:27,100
Mr. Xie,

31
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,860
can you bear the consequences?

32
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:31,700
I only know that for years,

33
00:02:31,820 --> 00:02:34,220
the Yang Family
has protected our borders.

34
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:36,620
As for you,

35
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:39,380
with your desire to marry Princess Pingyue,

36
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,380
you use the Yang Family

37
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:41,780
to sow discord,

38
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,300
hoping to up your status.

39
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:48,060
Mr. Xie is correct.

40
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:52,180
You may never know
what's under one's mask.

41
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:54,420
Mr. Wang resides in court.

42
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,340
You know little about our borders.

43
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:59,700
But the weapons used by our enemies

44
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:01,220
are mostly from the Great Xia.

45
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:03,180
Our soldiers saw it with their own eyes.

46
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:04,220
How will you

47
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:06,380
explain this matter?

48
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:08,180
In my humble opinion,

49
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:10,540
Mr. Xie is the one spewing lies.

50
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:16,260
What if the Yangs were sabotaged

51
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:18,740
and are truly innocent?

52
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:25,020
Your Majesty,

53
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:27,300
if the Yang Family is really framed,

54
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:28,380
all the more we should investigate.

55
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:29,460
Or else,

56
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:32,420
all loyal members of the Yang Family

57
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:35,220
will be haunted by rumors for eternity

58
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:36,820
with their names tainted.

59
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:38,380
Such is injustice, Your Majesty.

60
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:42,740
If everyone here truly respects
the Yang Family,

61
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:44,060
is this the result

62
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:46,940
you wish to see?

63
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:51,140
My subjects,

64
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:53,540
any other comments?

65
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:02,020
Well, with no other comments,

66
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:02,940
it is decided.

67
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:04,500
Since this involves the esteemed Yangs,

68
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:08,340
Pingyue will be in charge of this case.

69
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,420
Pei Wenxuan will be the Inspector Censor

70
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,660
and assist her with the case.

71
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,980
Since you two are involved
in this matter,

72
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:17,380
Su Rongqing will supervise.

73
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:21,220
What do we think of this?

74
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:24,300
Your Majesty is wise.

75
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:25,980
Draft the decree.

76
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:31,580
Good job.

77
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:35,180
Next, we'll have to talk reason
with the Yangs.

78
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:36,700
Will they listen?

79
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:39,260
Perhaps not to me,

80
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:40,540
but surely to you.

81
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:43,540
After all, being unreasonable
is your forte.

82
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,260
With the current situation,

83
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:55,260
Concubine Ning must have a plan.

84
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:59,740
The Yang Family has also earned
the people's hearts.

85
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:01,740
If we don't secure enough proof

86
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:03,500
before we search their residence,

87
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,780
we'll become the villains.

88
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:09,980
Mr. Su.

89
00:05:15,140 --> 00:05:15,820
Your Highness.

90
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:17,140
Mr. Su,

91
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:19,540
now is not the right time

92
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:22,100
to search the Yang Family's residence.

93
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,700
Hence, I want to find some ledgers

94
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:25,100
from the Bureau of Military Appointments.

95
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:27,020
Can you help me, Mr. Su?

96
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:29,540
As per your instructions.

97
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,100
I will have to trouble you

98
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,460
to liaise with the bureau.

99
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:33,900
I'll go if the bureau is willing

100
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:34,860
to check the ledgers.

101
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:35,860
Understood.

102
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:40,740
Good day, Mr. Su.

103
00:05:52,340 --> 00:05:54,100
Your wedding with the princess

104
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:55,340
must've been finalized.

105
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:58,580
I heard there was quite a ruckus
in the palace last night.

106
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:02,180
You seem to care a lot, Young Master Su.

107
00:06:02,180 --> 00:06:03,580
Who doesn't care about

108
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:08,220
the princess's wedding in the capital?

109
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:10,220
You're the hot topic in the capital

110
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:11,500
right now.

111
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:14,060
Hot topic? About what?

112
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:16,300
About whether I'll marry the princess?

113
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:19,140
Well, allow me to be frank.

114
00:06:19,980 --> 00:06:21,860
I will marry the princess.

115
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:28,060
I'm a little curious.

116
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:31,940
What do you think of the princess?

117
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:35,340
She is good.

118
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:36,980
She is eloquent.

119
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:38,780
More like harsh.

120
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,740
But I heard

121
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:43,020
you had an engagement
when you were a child.

122
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:45,460
How do you feel about that lady...?

123
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:52,620
I understand.

124
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,340
Some people are like the moon.

125
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:56,620
You may watch, but never touch.

126
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:01,900
Mr. Su,

127
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:04,140
please refrain from discussing
Her Highness.

128
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:06,060
Otherwise, I might become confused

129
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,300
about who you see as your moon.

130
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:13,460
Of course. I would never dare.

131
00:07:16,740 --> 00:07:18,580
I still have business with the princess.

132
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:20,300
Please excuse me.

133
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:22,820
See you next time, Mr. Pei.

134
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,140
What?

135
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:42,340
Inform everyone

136
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:44,420
to guard the residence.
No one is to leave.

137
00:07:45,020 --> 00:07:46,940
Also, send a letter to the border

138
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:47,820
for an urgent solution.

139
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:52,980
We're going to Hanqiu Palace.

140
00:07:58,140 --> 00:07:59,700
Su Rongqing is interested in you.

141
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,660
Aren't you as well?

142
00:08:01,460 --> 00:08:02,100
I...

143
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:06,300
I don't mind.

144
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:09,900
Remember Tuoba Yan?

145
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:15,180
The bank owner you once arrested?

146
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:16,340
Yes.

147
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:18,580
He travels among the states

148
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:20,020
and launders money for a living.

149
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:22,380
Many nobles in Huajing
are involved with him.

150
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:24,700
Including the Yangs.

151
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:29,100
Tuoba Yan

152
00:08:29,940 --> 00:08:31,460
is able to survive for so long

153
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:33,380
not because he's good at business,

154
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:35,460
but also because he has
a protective charm.

155
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:37,740
The ledgers.

156
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:42,220
So that's why you're taking your time
with the bureau's ledgers.

157
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:45,060
Something that's audited every year

158
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:45,980
cannot be the real deal.

159
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:51,900
If we obtain the ledger from Tuoba Yan

160
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:53,140
detailing their laundering acts,

161
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,420
we get to prove

162
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:56,740
the guilt of the Yangs.

163
00:08:58,740 --> 00:08:59,580
But what next?

164
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:01,460
Do you have any plans?

165
00:09:03,180 --> 00:09:04,900
We've cornered the Yangs.

166
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:06,780
General Yang may be at the front line,

167
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:08,220
but he got a distress signal for sure.

168
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:11,060
He'll threaten Father
with his resignation.

169
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:13,020
Don't worry about that.

170
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:14,020
His Majesty is prepared.

171
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,180
He has the Xiao Family taking care

172
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,140
of everything in the dark.

173
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:19,180
However,

174
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:21,300
the Xiaos cannot hold them back for long.

175
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:22,860
That why, on the surface,

176
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,780
the Crown Prince needs to take charge.

177
00:09:27,460 --> 00:09:30,860
Tomorrow, we'll go find
Qin Lin and Cui Qinghe.

178
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,420
They'll follow the Crown Prince to the front line.

179
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:35,180
We just need two more weeks.

180
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:36,940
When the enemies' weapons

181
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:37,980
are exhausted,

182
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:41,140
the Crown Prince will earn his merits.

183
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:48,580
Say...

184
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,780
if we weren't enemies in the past,

185
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:53,940
perhaps we would've been great partners.

186
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,300
Don't you think?

187
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:59,180
If it weren't for your beloved,

188
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:01,020
we would've remained husband and wife.

189
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:06,060
I wish to see His Majesty!

190
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:06,780
Out of my way!

191
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:07,660
Your Highness,

192
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:10,900
His Majesty has ordered
he does not wish to see you.

193
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:13,660
If you act rashly,

194
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,660
you will only anger His Majesty more.

195
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:20,420
Your Highness.

196
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:37,020
[Hanqiu Palace]
We guarded the borders for generations!

197
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:39,780
We serve the nation,
producing only the loyalest of warriors!

198
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:42,900
Your Majesty!
Believe not the words of villains!

199
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:44,900
If Your Majesty refuses to see me,

200
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,420
I will kneel here forever!

201
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:47,780
Be it a day

202
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:49,380
or a year!

203
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:52,420
Until Your Majesty is willing to see me!

204
00:10:58,380 --> 00:10:58,900
Halt.

205
00:11:01,700 --> 00:11:03,420
Your Highness, it's Feng Ming.

206
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,580
Ask her to come up.

207
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:12,900
Your Highness.

208
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:15,060
This is a private invitation
to Tuoba Yan's banquet.

209
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:18,420
These are clothes
prepared by the Crown Prince

210
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:19,540
and the trade contract.

211
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:22,660
Alright, you may go.

212
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:26,420
The Crown Prince is worried
about your safety.

213
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:29,180
Tuoba Yan has complex ties.

214
00:11:29,540 --> 00:11:30,820
His residence may not be safe.

215
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:33,380
Are you really going to risk it?

216
00:11:34,180 --> 00:11:35,940
It's okay. I have the whistling arrow.

217
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:39,420
But the Crown Prince

218
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:40,900
ordered me to accompany you.

219
00:11:47,020 --> 00:11:47,660
Alright.

220
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:50,180
I will wait outside.

221
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:58,140
Wake up.

222
00:12:04,420 --> 00:12:05,260
Get up!

223
00:12:07,860 --> 00:12:13,020
♪A dream, takes me through eternity♪

224
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:16,140
It's been so many years,

225
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:17,580
yet you still love

226
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:18,540
to sleep in.

227
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:20,820
I suppose I can help.

228
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:23,300
♪Only wrinkles on one's sleeves♪

229
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:25,700
Pei Wenxuan, get up!

230
00:12:25,700 --> 00:12:27,500
♪Then, you wave to me♪

231
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:29,220
Wake up, Pei Wenxuan.

232
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:31,300
♪I follow the breeze♪

233
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:34,100
♪And I see your eyes♪

234
00:12:34,100 --> 00:12:36,900
Wake up, or you'll be late to court.

235
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:37,780
Get up.

236
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:38,580
♪Parasol trees by the garden♪

237
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:39,820
♪With a pen, one weaves a view♪

238
00:12:39,820 --> 00:12:41,220
Get up. Get up.

239
00:12:41,220 --> 00:12:42,900
Get up. Get up. Get up.

240
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:47,420
♪I'm glad to have you in my world♪

241
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:49,820
♪By my side♪

242
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:50,900
Are you getting up?

243
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:55,420
♪We watch the moon and sun♪

244
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:58,060
♪We watch fate♪

245
00:12:58,060 --> 00:12:59,060
♪We climb the high tower♪

246
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:01,180
One more time, are you getting up?

247
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:02,900
Just a bit longer.

248
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:04,420
Fine.

249
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:06,020
♪Then we light up a lantern somewhere♪

250
00:13:06,300 --> 00:13:09,980
♪The years pass♪

251
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:12,180
♪History may repeat♪

252
00:13:12,180 --> 00:13:12,940
Stop sleeping.

253
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:16,740
♪I know you will be with me♪

254
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:22,500
I'm awake.

255
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,100
On the 10th day of each month,

256
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:40,620
Tuoba Yan hosts a private banquet
in his mansion,

257
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:42,420
inviting tycoons from various nations.

258
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:44,020
Today is the 10th day.

259
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:47,140
I drew this based on my memory.

260
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:48,420
Familiarize yourself with it.

261
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:50,980
Are you going?

262
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:55,140
Have the hidden guards do it.

263
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:57,580
You're a princess.

264
00:13:57,580 --> 00:13:58,820
What if something happens?

265
00:13:58,820 --> 00:13:59,980
That wouldn't be ideal.

266
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:04,420
I know I'm delicate.

267
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:07,060
There are traps in his room.

268
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:09,420
You can only enter
by pressing the right button.

269
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:11,180
Persian is written on the button.

270
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,580
Do our secret guards know Persian?

271
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:17,660
Yes, our dear princess

272
00:14:17,780 --> 00:14:19,100
learned Persian for her marriage

273
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:20,420
to the West.

274
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:30,020
Who knew

275
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:32,580
you would have such a unique skill?

276
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:33,300
Hmm?

277
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:39,740
Are you nervous for me?

278
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:44,140
I'm just worried about myself.

279
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:46,340
If something did happen to you,

280
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:47,180
I'll be dead too.

281
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:52,540
I like that logic.

282
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:54,940
