military command,

683
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:34,180
leaving me to brave the hell fire alone,

684
00:37:34,980 --> 00:37:36,380
cleaning up the mess.

685
00:37:40,540 --> 00:37:43,700
Since we have the chance to restart,

686
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:46,100
of course I'd prefer

687
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:47,540
to make this life better.

688
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:52,060
In the end,

689
00:37:52,060 --> 00:37:53,780
you were paving your path,
Prime Minister Pei.

690
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:56,900
Looks like I thought too much.

691
00:37:57,700 --> 00:38:00,060
When you said you'd get me
the military command,

692
00:38:01,060 --> 00:38:02,260
