to your grave.

701
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:24,180
Let's make a wager then.

702
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:27,980
If you can truly fall for me,

703
00:38:30,900 --> 00:38:31,660
I...

704
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:34,580
will give you my life.

705
00:38:50,660 --> 00:38:51,500
Alright.

706
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:54,220
I've got to visit Qin Lin
at Jiulu Mountain tomorrow.

707
00:38:54,740 --> 00:38:55,740
I'll take my leave.

708
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:03,740
But frankly speaking,

709
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:07,900
